sentence: In trading on Monday, shares of Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD) crossed below their 200 day moving average of $78.10, changing hands as low as $77.37 per share.
Home Depot Inc shares are currently trading down about 1.7% on the day.

The chart below shows the one year performance of HD shares, versus its 200 day moving average:

Looking at the chart above, HD's low point in its 52 week range is $69.78 per share, with $83.20 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $77.23.
According to the ETF Finder at ETF Channel, HD makes up 7.43% of the Retail ETF (Symbol: RTH) which is trading lower by about 0.7% on the day Monday.
